Celestia
Celestia - Last Edited: 2008-04-11 14:09:16 by Blaize
=====================================================
Celestia, or the Celestial Plane is a great expanse of
the heavens reachable only through portals in the
Ethereal or Astral Planes. Celestia is a war ground
between the forces of good and evil as heavenly and
demonic creatures vying for control of the area for
eons. Angels, Titans, Dragons, and Demons are in a
constant state of battle throughout the majority of
the plane.
Notably, the great Titan Palace, and Lord of all Titankin
Cronus can be found here, as well as the gates of Hell
themselves, protected by the three-headed hellhound,
Cerberus. Though much evil and devastation is abound in
Celestia, the being called Malevolence is a force of
such power and anarchy his plan to destroy the Lifestream
threatens the balance of all, heavenly and mortal alike.
