Karma
Karma - Last Edited: 2008-03-25 20:06:41 by Blaize
==================================================
Karma is a mystical sum of the actions of a living soul.  It is believed that
through actions deemed as morally positive, one will be met by similarly
positive actions.  The opposite of course being that if one is morally negative
that only negative actions will that soul meet.  Karma is not the same as fate,
as all who live make decisions that affect themselves.  Karma is merely a way
of expressing the whole of one's actions throughout a lifetime.  Karma has an
indirect effect upon a soul that is guided by that soul's decisions; for better
or for worse.
