Artifact
Artifact - Last Edited: 2017-09-19 00:43:26 by lohrr
====================================================
Artifacts are the premier weapons, armor, and items in the game.  Each
artifact or arti, has its own special characteristics, which make each
one, one of a kind. One could consider obtaining and owning an artifact a
great accomplishment. Though watch your back, other players desire them
as much if not more than you do...
Players are expected to hold artis they obtain. However, they do not need
to drag the artifact around on characters that cannot wield/use them.
As an example, you sorcerer can be using the staff of blue flames and
your paladin can be running around with avernus.
The best way to avoid problems is to not be greedy.  Artifacts are not meant to be
