be used if the player you want to converse with is the same room.  "Tell"
is for global communication.  You can "tell" anyone who is awake, is not
in a dark room or invis and has tell on, no matter where they are in the
mud.
Please do not ask the Staff to tell a person that you can't reply to them.
You will have to wait until they are visible and do it yourself.
Note:  "tell" is a user command, and is only available to make the game
more playable.
