  auc offer sword 10 50
* To auction the sword for 10 plat with a 4 day timer, or someone can buy it now for 50 plat:
  auc offer sword 10 50 4
* To auction 5 of the sword for 10 plat with a 4 day timer, or someone can buy it now for 50 plat
  auc offer sword 10 50 4 5
