Players can access the auction services from generally anywhere they
find themselves in the world of Duris. Auctions are an amazing way to
acquire high level equipment with minimal effort.
The global auctioning committee has worked long and arduously
coordinating Human, Halfling, Orc, and Duergar Dwarf
efforts to allow this civilized form of bartering. In order to maximize
