* Shady Grove: Auction Mound
Auction commands can be abbreviated to one letter (for example: instead
of "auction list sort head" you can type "auc l s head")
The currently available commands at auction houses are:
* auction list: see what is available at the auction
* auction offer: offer something to be sold at auction
* auction bid: place a bid
* auction info: find out stats on an item that is up for auction
* auction pickup: pickup items or cash from the auction house
These commands are available at any time, except for a short period after
removing a worn piece of equipment.
