After the death of your character, you will return to the game without your
personal items. To get your items back, you have to travel to the location
where you died and retrieve your corpse. Your items will be on your corpse,
unless they have been looted by someone else.
A cr can be simple, or it can be very time-consuming and complicated. It is
always a wise move to leave a ''sitter'' if you are doing a difficult zone.
Please see help rules.
