Epic - Last Edited: 2015-09-18 16:37:13 by lohrr
================================================
The epics needed to progress past level 50 are as follows...
* 51:  1000 + touch Charcoal Palace, The Great Shaboath, or Lost Temple of Tikitzopl
* 52:  2500 + touch Plane of Fire-Brass, Githzerai Stronghold or Temple of Earth.
* 53:  4500 + touch Ceothia or Tiamat
* 54:  7000 + touch Bahamut's Palace, Apocalypse Castle or Vecna's tomb
* 55: 10000 + touch Negative Material Plane or Bronze Citadel
* 56: 13500 + touch Celestial Plane, Castle Ravenloft, Ny'Neth Stronghold Continued or
   The 222nd Layer of the Abyss
You can gain these epic points from either finding and touching the many runestones and monoliths hidden about the land, or by tasting the blood of your enemies.
From level 51 onwards, you must seek out a specific stone (listed above)  and touch it to receive the level.  You may also level by accruing 2x the required amount of epics, then touching any stone.  The cost to you will remain the same. You will not be charged double epics for touching a runestone that is not specific to your level.
**Multi-classes no longer need double epics to level.**
