Ship Crews
=========================================
In port towns around the world look around the places sailor gather to have fun or settle deals.
You will find whole crews and principal crew members looking for employment.
Typing 'list' in such places will show you available crews, their specialty and experience.
The better crew is, the more demanding it is to their new captain. There are two ways to meet
their requirements. First is to be at least somewhat famous as a captain (to have a certain
amount of ship frags). Second is to be currently employing a crew, that has higher skill in every
area, than basic skill of the crew you want to hire.
The chief members you can hire are leaders of the crew in one of the aspects of ship handling.
Having these guys aboard helps your crew grow faster in experience and perform their duties better.
They will only work for you if you meet their requirements or your current crew is above certain
skill level in their area.
