====================================================
A sitter is someone who has been given the glamorous role of doing nothing but sitting in a port room of a zone. The sitter helps ensure that if the rest of group dies, e.g. massrips, that the zone will not ''pop'', and that the group members can quickly port up to the sitter, ensuring a much more expedient ''cr''.
As a sitter, it is important not to fall asleep or go watch a movie, thus letting your character idle out, leaving your group without a sitter.
Sitters also serve an additional role, acting as an early warning system for enemy groups. Sitters are usually the first to die in zone hits, but will alert the group to prepare for combat. After being alerted of an enemy presence, the group's chances of survival are greatly increased.
