Snarl is a social command, or an Emote. Typing this command will allow you to Snarl at someone in anger, using preprogrammed commands. The benefits of using these commands will allow you in one word to sum up a long phrase, and social commands are sometimes used as triggers. More often they are a nice simple command to express yourself. The command list is as follows.
