Sneak
Sneak - Last Edited: 2007-04-19 19:17:15 by Unknown
===================================================
Sneak allows you to move silently from one place to
another.
==Syntax==
 sneak
 sneak off
==Description==
A person who sneaks successfully will be able to travel
(for a period of time) without anyone taking notice of his
or her arrival or departure. As with most learned skills,
there is always a chance that you will not sneak
successfully and, with this particular command, you will
be unable to tell if it has worked or not. You can quit
sneaking with "sneak off"
