Sneer
Sneer - Last Edited: 2007-04-22 22:12:53 by Unknown
===================================================
Sneer is a social command used to show your lack of respect
for another player, mob or a situation.  Sneering is the
slight raising of the upper lip to show the top set of teeth.
Sneering does not require a target, but sneering at someone
can let them know you are displeased.  A sneer can also have
a sexual connotation that is unmistakeable to a character of
the other gender.
